casebody.data:
Wednesday, August 27, 1997

RECONSIDERATION DOCKET

97-795. GTE N., Inc. v. Pub. Util. Comm.

Public Utilities Commission, No. 95-845-TP-COI. Reported at'79 Ohio St.3d 1466, 681 N.E.2d 938.

Upon consideration of appellant’s motion for reconsideration of the dismissal of this case for want of prosecution,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the motion for reconsideration be, and hereby is, denied.

Resnick, J., not participating.
